{"tid":2127290,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"17歲學生承認管有物品意圖損壞財產罪　判60小時社會服務令","createTime":"2020-07-27T08:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T10:00:20.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc0fe23098989518d2a3456649235b51bccc2a6","tid":2127290,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540113-20200727.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540113-20200727.htm&d=ducsj56GsZITs%2BYA0ylwpX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=3c840b7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540113-20200727.htm&h=a3f1f5d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540113-20200727.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n一名17歲學生去年11月在將軍澳被截查時，被搜出1支噴漆，他早前承認管有物品意圖損壞財產罪，今日在觀塘法院被判60小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n被告孫煜希被控於去年11月13日在將軍澳寶順路與翠嶺路交界管有一支噴漆，意圖在無合法辯解的情況下使用該物品，以損壞其他人的財產。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官表示，感化報告指，被告已有父母從旁協助，不適合感化令，短時間的社會服務令更為合適，因此判處被告60小時社會服務令。"},{"pid":"128a8842e030b25869fcd312d47a042ecbf36201","tid":2127290,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:53:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82079af6f25ed02b5428899d15bf9b742e733e49","tid":2127290,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T08:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec63cac554c23d029c80a7a90c5de8e5bcfd3ce","tid":2127290,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T09:00:47.000Z","msg":"等睇律政司上訴要求改判監禁"},{"pid":"67ffbb3031d64f707968b7ec6d1fb70f96708026","tid":21272